app.use(morgan('combined')); // or use a structured logger like winston/pino
```

#### 10. Port Hardcoded (Minor)
Port `3000` is hardcoded. Prefer environment-driven configuration:
```js
const PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
