#### 11. No Error Handling Middleware
Unhandled errors may leak stack traces or internal details to clients:
```js
// Place this LAST, after all routes
app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  console.error(err.stack); // log internally
  res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal Server Error' }); // never expose err.message
});
```

